description:
Danny is back earlier than planned from his hiatus because he couldn't go another minute without recapping the iconic Vanderpump Rules season trailer with Hannah Brown (host of the Brown-Eyed Jewnicorn podcast). They discuss every frame of footage Bravo released, plus hopes for the upcoming season, and lots more.


*For bonus episodes & to support this podcast, visit Patreon.com/EverythingIconic
